# Domain Layer (`packages/domain`)

## Imports — FORBIDDEN

FastAPI, Celery, SQLAlchemy, Neo4j drivers, Redis, provider SDKs, UI code.

## Allowed

- Pydantic models for domain types and value objects
- Pure Python logic, enums, domain exceptions
- No I/O, no framework dependencies

## Patterns

- Opaque UUIDs for all domain object IDs
- Source identity via `(source_id, external_id)` separate from UUID
- Claim lifecycle: `proposed → approved → active → superseded | rejected | retracted`
- Immutable `SourceObjectVersion` with content hash

See `docs/04-domain-model-and-ontology.md` for aggregates and relationships.
